Might not be a font. Note the ® for the conjoined BA.  
No commercial matches at Myfonts or Linotype thar I could spot.  
Somewhat similar style for [SF Wasabi](http://web.archive.org/web/20140724103906/http:/www.dafont.com/sf-wasabi.font?fpp=50).  
More faux Chinese & Japanese fonts at:  
 [http://www.dafont.com/theme.php?cat=201&fpp=50](http://web.archive.org/web/20140724103906/http:/www.dafont.com/theme.php?cat=201&fpp=50 "http://www.dafont.com/theme.php?cat=201&fpp=50")  
I checked other sites with large collections of faux Chinese & Japanese fonts & also did not see a match.  
In the other hand, further searching might turn up a match.  
Don
